com.google.wave.api.event
Interface Event

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractEvent, AnnotatedTextChangedEvent, BlipContributorsChangedEvent, BlipSubmittedEvent, DocumentChangedEvent, FormButtonClickedEvent, GadgetStateChangedEvent, OperationErrorEvent, WaveletBlipCreatedEvent, WaveletBlipRemovedEvent, WaveletCreatedEvent, WaveletFetchedEvent, WaveletParticipantsChangedEvent, WaveletSelfAddedEvent, WaveletSelfRemovedEvent, WaveletTitleChangedEvent
public interface Event

Object describing a single event, that captures changes made to a wavelet or blip in a wave.

Method Summary
